  "about": {
    "details": "<p>Kesar India Limited is engaged in the business of <strong>developing and constructing residential and commercial projects, industrial buildings, factory buildings, workshop buildings,</strong> etc. All the projects are marketed under the brand name, \"Kesar Lands\".</p>\n<p>As of December 31, 2021, it has a total land reserve of 123.70 lakh square feet. It has successfully completed many projects such as Kesar Vihar, Kesar Shree, Kesar Garden, and Kesar Signature projects. Kesar Gateway is its ongoing project while Kesar Forest, Kesar Exotica, Kesar Tower, Kesar Hills, and Kesar Imperial are some of the upcoming projects.</p>\n<p><strong>Competitive strengths</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Complete project management from land acquisition to conceptualization and marketing.</li>\n<li>Experienced team of managers.</li>\n<li>Stringent quality standards and compliance.</li>\n</ul>"
  },
